3ï¸âƒ£ TWO TYPES (ONLY THESE)
ğŸ”¹ A) FIXED WINDOW

âœ” Window size = k is given

Examples

Max sum of subarray of size k

Average of size k

Pattern

window_sum = sum(arr[:k])
answer = window_sum

for i in range(k, n):
    window_sum += arr[i]
    window_sum -= arr[i-k]
    answer = max(answer, window_sum)


ğŸ§  Memory line:

